data.description: Better than NEW, this 2022 luxury Tampa Heights townhome is a true showstopper with a contemporary aesthetic, highlighted by designer upgrades throughout - just minutes to Downtown Tampa and the Riverwalk! The possibilities are endless with NO HOA lease or short-term rental restrictions and commercial zoning – ideal for a home office (2nd entrance and signage allowed!), Airbnb, long-term investment, or enjoy the intimate community feel and make this your home sweet home! The ideal layout offers an open concept living area, bedroom, full bathroom, laundry, and pantry all on the first floor. As you make your way upstairs, you will find an oversized primary suite with en-suite bath and 3rd bedroom with attached bath. Enjoy the privacy of your own fully fenced and turfed backyard, newly installed in 2023, perfect for your morning cup of coffee or your furry friends! Premium upgrades galore in this home – no builder grade here! The elevated interior includes upgraded Samsung kitchen appliances, LG smart washer & dryer, quartz countertops, soft close cabinetry, tile backsplash, kitchen island wainscoting, designer light fixtures, contemporary sink and faucets, premier custom paint, consistent Cortec flooring, custom crown molding & baseboards, all new modernized shower heads, handles, towel racks, faucets and comfort height toilets in all bathrooms, custom Alpha shelving in all bedroom closets, pantry and laundry room, and custom electric blinds with 20% window tint. This townhome community is also eco-friendly with National Green Building Standard Rating and includes 2 reserved parking spaces per unit. Located in one of the most highly desired Tampa locations - see Downtown Tampa from your front door! Don’t miss out on owning a slice of the best of Tampa Bay, bikeable to Downtown, the Riverwalk, and Armature Works, and just minutes from Sparkman Wharf, Tampa International Airport, Hyde Park and more.
